                    <li>Security and access control</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="admin-info">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #007bff;">Welcome Back to Administration</h3>
                <p>Your administrative access has been fully restored. You can now log in and resume your administrative duties.</p>
                <p>All your previous administrative privileges and permissions have been reinstated.</p>
            </div>
            
