            <p>Thank you for your patience, and welcome back to the Simply MOT administrative team!</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>Simply MOT System Administration</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated administrative notification. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>Simply MOT - Administrative Security Protocol</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
